@startuml
title UC-FR-06 Module Management
left to right direction

actor "Administrator" as Admin

rectangle "Academic Management System" {
  (View Modules) as View
  (Create Module) as Create
  (Edit Module) as Edit

  (Validate Module Data) as Validate
  (Reject Module Operation) as Reject
}

Admin -- View
Admin -- Create
Admin -- Edit

Create ..> Validate : <<include>>
Edit ..> Validate : <<include>>
Reject ..> Create : <<extend>>
Reject ..> Edit : <<extend>>

note right of Reject
Triggered when:
- course does not exist
- module code not unique
- module not linked to valid course
end note

@enduml
